# Build-context hygiene for `docker.exe build ./agent-service`.
#
# CRITICAL (WSL symlink gotcha): docker.exe chokes on this repo's WSL symlinks (every CLAUDE.md is
# a symlink to AGENTS.md). This build context is `./agent-service` and ships no such symlink, but
# the exclusion is kept defensively so a stray symlink can never break the build.
**/CLAUDE.md

# Regenerated inside the image / host-only artifacts.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
*.egg-info/

# Docs/build outputs that don't belong in the image.
README.md
data/README.md

# Host-side J4 live-demo driver + its evidence. The demo page HTML lives IN the image
# (app/demo_router.py); these scripts run on the host, so keep them out of the build context.
demo/
